<p class="">I have read that report and other reports which are not, I think, inconsistent with anything that I myself said yesterday, but it is my belief that, from the point of view of making progress, I should be wise to say nothing more at the moment.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
